<view class="page"><view class="nav" style="padding-top:{{navTop}}px;height:{{navHeight}}px"><view bindtap="goBack"><image src="{{icons.back}}"/><text>返回审核</text></view></view><scroll-view class="scroll" scroll-y enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}"><view style="height:{{navSpacer}}px"></view><view class="content"><view class="headline"><view>×</view><view><text>驳回申请</text><text>请填写驳回原因，申请人将收到通知</text></view></view>
<view class="panel"><view class="section-title">申请信息</view><view class="applicant"><image src="{{avatar}}" mode="aspectFill"/><view><view><text>林浩</text><text>病假</text></view><text>U10 提高班</text><text>◷ 7月16日（周二）18:30</text><text>原因：发烧咳嗽，医生建议休息</text></view><view class="proof"><text>医院证明</text><text>已上传</text></view><view><text>待审核</text><text>提交时间</text><text>7月15日 16:42</text></view></view></view>
<view class="panel form-panel"><view class="section-title">选择驳回原因</view><view class="reasons"><view class="reason {{item.activeClass}}" wx:for="{{reasons}}" wx:key="key" data-value="{{item.key}}" bindtap="selectReason"><text>{{item.icon}}</text><text>{{item.title}}</text><view>{{item.mark}}</view></view></view><view class="section-title small">补充说明 <text>（选填）</text></view><textarea maxlength="200" placeholder="请详细说明驳回原因，便于申请人了解。" value="{{detail}}" bindinput="inputDetail"/><text class="count">{{detail.length}}/200</text><view class="section-title small">是否允许重新提交</view><view class="permissions"><view class="permission {{item.activeClass}}" wx:for="{{permissions}}" wx:key="key" data-value="{{item.key}}" bindtap="selectPermission"><view><text>{{item.title}}</text><text>{{item.note}}</text></view><text>{{item.mark}}</text></view></view>
<view class="notify"><view class="section-title small">通知对象</view><view><text>♢</text><view><text>将通知以下人员</text><text>✓ 申请人（林浩）　✓ 学员家长　✓ 相关教练　✓ 课程顾问</text></view></view></view></view>
<view class="buttons"><view bindtap="goBack">返回审核</view><view bindtap="confirm">➤　确认驳回并通知</view></view><view class="safe"></view></view></scroll-view></view>
